Many of the most effective drugs are not known or are not well known because of the difficulty of developing and controlling these drugs or their compounds.
Currently, due to the lack of a specific treatment for COVID-19, TCM has become one of the most effective complementary treatments for patients with mild to moderate symptoms or patients who have recovered.
For example, Shu Feng Jie Du and Lian Hua Qing Wen drops have been shown to be potentially useful in the treatment of COVID-19.
High recovery rates in treating COVID-19 patients were observed in many provinces in China that used TCM in 87% of local patients, such as Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) and Hunan (50%), and Hubei Province, which used TCM in only about 30% of COVID-19 patients, with the lowest recovery rate (13%).
